            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De spe et desperatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
      ¶ De spe et desperatione. Rubrica. 5.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>SAlomon in prouerbiis
      <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>1. c. 13. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e125">Spes quae
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>Idiffertur affligat animam.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e131"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e133"> 27. c. Ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>glorieris in crastinum: ignorans quid
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>superuentura pariat dies. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e146">¶ Regum l. 2. c. 2. An ignoras quod periculo
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>sa sit desperatio. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e156">¶ Aristotelis retho. l. i. c. 20. Speranti conse
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>quitur fantasia aliqua eius quod sperat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e162"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e164"> Li. 2
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>c. 16. Iuuenes bone spei sunt. Iuuenes pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>pterea quod nondum in multis repulsam passi sunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>viuunt secundum plurima spei: spes quidem futuri
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>est: memoria autem preteriti: iuuenibus autem quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>quidem futurum multum: preteritum autem breue. Iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>uenes facile seductibiles sunt: sperant enim fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>cile. Senes difficilis spei sunt: propter expe
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>rientiam. plura enim eorum que fiunt mala sunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>eueniunt enim multa indeterius. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e187">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e191">¶ Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 22. Ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>amicum et si produxeris gladium ne desperes. est
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>enim regressus ad amicum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e199">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e203">¶ Oratius in epistolis. vel. i. e. 4. Grata super
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>ueniet que non sperabitur hora. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e209">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e213">¶ Tullius inuectiuarum in catilinam vel. 4. et fi.
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>Spes sola hominem in minseriis consolari solet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e220">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e224">¶ Ouidius epistolaru. 2. e. Quecumque ex meri
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>to spes venit: equa venit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e230">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e234">/ Epistola. 16
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>Fallitur augurio spes bona sepe suo </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e240">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e244">/ Idem methamorph. li.
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>Spes tantu in dubio est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e250">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e254">/ Libro. 9.
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>Spes est que cupiarspes est qui pascat amantem </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e260">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e264">/ Idem de ponto vel. 3. e. 7. et antepenul.
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>Spem iuuat amplecti: que non iuuat irrita sper
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>Et fieri cupias si qua futura putes. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e272">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e276">¶ Quintilianus delcamationum. 7 declam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>Nihil magis. interesse hominum puto quam vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>spes pro homine tam longa quam vita sit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e285">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e289">¶ Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. l. 2. e. 3. Spes
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>incerti boni nomen est. / Li. 12 e. 2. et f. Di
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>uitie insolentiam dant: nihil est aliud insolen
        <lb ed="#V" n="44" break="no"/>tia quam spes false magnitudinis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e299"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e301"> Li. 18 e. i.
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>O quanta dementia est spes longas inchoam <!--277.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>tium. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e313"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e315"> Idem declamationuml. 5 causa. i. Spes.
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>vltimum est aduersarum rerum solatium. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e321"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e323"> Li.
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>9. c. 6. et fi. Concitatissima est rabies in de
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>speratione. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e331"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e333"> Idem de breuitate vite. Spes
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>spem excitat ambitionem ambitio. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e339">
               <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e343">¶ Lucanus. vel. i. Spes saltem trepidas men
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>tes leuat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e350">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e354">¶ Ualerius maximus vel 6 ti. 9. et fi. Stultum
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>est perpetue infelicitati se damnare spemque
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>ex incerto recte fouetur interdum certam in de
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>sperationem conuertere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e364">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e368">¶ Statius thebaidos l. 2. Non grauior mor
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>talibus addita cura Spex vbi longa venit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e374">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e378">¶ Uegetius de re mi li. l. 3 ti. 10. Nemo de
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>speret fieri posse que facta sunt. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e384"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e386"> Lib. 3 ti.
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>et 3 Ex despera: ione crescit audacia: et cum
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>spei nihil est sumit arma formido. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e394">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e398">¶ Augustinus in epigram mnatibus prospe
        <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>ri emp. 86 Non est desperandum de ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>lis: sed pro ipsis vt boni fiant potius suppli
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>candum: quia numerus sanctorum semper est
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>auctus de numero impiorum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e410">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e414">¶ Cato. capitulo 3. Spem retine: spes vna
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>hominem nec morte reliquit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e421">
               <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e425">/ Capitulo. 5. et fi.
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>In aduersis melius sperare memento. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e431">¶
      <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e435">¶ Boetius. lib. diuisionum: Quis non vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>deat plurimum ad bonarum artium defe
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>ctum valere: si apud mentes hominum numquam
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>sit desperatio discendi. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e445">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e449">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum vel. 4. e. 25. In ipsis
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>conatibus egra languescunt: que meritorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>presumptionibus non inuuantur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e457">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e461">¶ Isydorus in synon. solliloquiorum l. i. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>Desperatio auget peccatum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e467">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e471">¶ Uersificator fabularum esopi. 29 fa. Sic
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>timeat quicumque timet ne molle timoris.
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>Spe careat: grauis est spe fugiente timor.
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>Speret qui metuit: morituros viuere vidi:
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>Spe duce: victuros spe moriente mori. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e483">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e487">¶ Auctor vel qui dicitur pamphylus. c. i.
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Spes reficit dominum: fallit et ipsa suum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e494">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e498">/ Capitulo. 13
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>Obstitit interdum factis fortuna virorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>Propositumque suo non sinit esse loco. <!--278.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="120-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e512">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e516">/ Capitulo 36
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>Desperare nocet: votum labor improbus. implet.
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>Capitulo 37
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>Sorte sub ambigua spes et labor omnis habetur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>Crescit principio spes tantum ipsa bono. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e528">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e532">¶ Baldo. 11 fabula. Hic ope virtutis spes
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>est vbi nulla salutis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e538">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e542">¶ Gualterius de castellione l. 7. Spes in du
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>biis semper comes optima rebus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e548">
               <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e552">¶ Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 5 6. Spes bo
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>na mortales fallere sepe solet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e558">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e562">¶ Auctor scili de moribus medicorum. c. 11.
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>Spes mulios decipit. atque
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>Hec eadem reficit: implet: et euacuat. </quote>
            </p>
    
         </div>
